# Frontend RMI

## Design Tokens (jangan hardcode warna)

```tsx
// ✅ Gunakan token Tailwind
<button className="bg-primary hover:bg-primary-dark text-white" />
<p className="text-foreground" />
<div className="bg-surface rounded-rmi shadow-soft" />

// ❌ Hindari hex langsung di komponen
<button className="bg-[#4e830a]" />
```

Token: `primary`, `primary-dark`, `primary-light`, `secondary`, `background`, `surface`, `foreground`, `heading`, `accent-green`.

Font: Poppins via `font-sans` (sudah di root layout).

## Struktur File

| Path | Isi |
|------|-----|
| `src/components/ui/` | Primitif reusable (Button, Card, Input) |
| `src/components/layout/` | Navbar, Footer |
| `src/components/home/` | Section beranda |
| `src/data/mock/` | Mock data (fase visual) |
| `src/lib/` | Utils, API client, fonts |
| `src/types/` | TypeScript types |
| `src/app/(public)/` | Halaman publik |

## Komponen UI

- Props dengan TypeScript interface
- Variant via props (`variant`, `size`), bukan class string di parent
- Export dari `src/components/ui/index.ts` jika banyak komponen
- Preview komponen baru di `/design-system`

## Next.js

- App Router, server components default
- `"use client"` hanya jika perlu state/event/hooks
- `next/image` untuk gambar produksi
- Metadata di `layout.tsx` atau `generateMetadata`
